    <div class="body">
        <p>At the moment _loadTranslationData ignores the include_path:</p>

<p>protected function _loadTranslationData($filename, $locale, array $options = array())
{
/*       ....................*/
        $this-&gt;_file = @fopen($filename, 'rb');
/*       ....................*/
}</p>

<p>May be change it to:</p>

<p>protected function _loadTranslationData($filename, $locale, array $options = array())
{
/*       ....................*/
        $this-&gt;_file = @fopen($filename, 'rb', true);
/*       ....................*/
}</p>

